{"title":"淞沪铁路","authors":["毛炳甫"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":8,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"淞沪铁路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛炳甫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一卷史书摊在大地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两行字写了一个世纪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在枕木的方格中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪烁着血的光，火的字。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把往事追溯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悲壮的歌铺了几十公里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一寸土地上的热血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流进了民族的记忆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轨道上有野马践踏过的蹄迹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"道钉下有泥土裹着的弹片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"品尝往昔甜酸苦辣的滋味；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心灵，经受了一次血的洗礼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨天的路九曲十八湾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天的路更自该珍惜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这英雄史书的第二卷；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我们从每一个黎明写起……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}